{"tid":944540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"烏克蘭總統無意延長戒嚴令","createTime":"2018-12-17T08:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T08:24:07.000Z","uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fa2d962f8c4d6c91836ca51f33f2875fa4ccb870","tid":944540,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:22:36.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭總統科羅申科說, 除非俄羅斯有大規模攻擊擊, 否則他無計劃延長戒嚴令.<br />\n<br />\n上月25日俄羅斯在克里米亞半島對開水域扣押3艘烏克蘭船隻及船員後, 科羅申科在烏克蘭部分地區實施戒嚴令一個月, 期間俄羅斯在接壤烏克蘭邊境加強軍事部署, 加劇兩國的緊張關係. 俄羅斯仍未釋放被扣押的烏克蘭船員, 並向他們作出檢控.<br />\n<br />\n波羅申科表示, 自戒嚴令實施後, 俄羅斯只將大約一成部隊由邊境撤走.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20181217014018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20181217014018&d=bVhSs0u1UTjocNzuugnzMMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=594eb70a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20181217014018</a>"},{"pid":"89c97d50f21444ccfcecec3dfc293a694320b27a","tid":944540,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"冇人 backup 烏克蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}